      <title>沙特阿美看到中国需求增长，寻求更多投资</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/aramco-chief-sees-healthy-chinese-demand-looking-more-investments-2024-03-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿美首席执行官阿明·纳赛尔周日表示，该石油巨头正在寻找在中国投资的更多机会，他表示中国的石油需求强劲且不断增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/aramco-chief-sees-healthy-chinese-demand-looking-more-investments-2024-03-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 09:10:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚洪水、山体滑坡已造成19人死亡、7人失踪</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-floods-landslide-kill-19-with-seven-missing-2024-03-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当局周日表示，连日暴雨导致印度尼西亚西苏门答腊省发生洪水和山体滑坡，迫使7万多人疏散，造成至少19人死亡，7人失踪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-floods-landslide-kill-19-with-seven-missing-2024-03-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 06:20:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚贸易部长称中国葡萄酒和龙虾贸易壁垒取得良好进展</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/good-progress-chinese-wine-lobster-trade-barriers-says-australia-trade-minister-2024-03-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚贸易部长唐·法雷尔周日表示，中国将在三月底之前完成对澳大利亚葡萄酒长达数年的关税审查，并正在审查对龙虾进口的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/good-progress-chinese-wine-lobster-trade-barriers-says-australia-trade-minister-2024-03-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 00:19:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦前总统扎尔达里连任</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistans-former-president-zardari-wins-another-term-2024-03-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[选举主持人表示，巴基斯坦前总统阿西夫·阿里·扎尔达里周六在议会和地区议会的投票中赢得了执政联盟的支持，赢得了第二个任期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistans-former-president-zardari-wins-another-term-2024-03-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 13:46:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>葡萄酒供过于求，澳大利亚农民砍掉了数百万棵葡萄藤</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australian-farmers-rip-out-millions-vines-amid-wine-glut-2024-03-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚数以百万计的葡萄藤正在被毁坏，还必须拔掉数以千万计的葡萄藤，以控制生产过剩，这种生产过剩已经压低了葡萄价格，并威胁到种植者和酿酒师的生计。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australian-farmers-rip-out-millions-vines-amid-wine-glut-2024-03-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 01:15:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚东南部遭遇热浪，森林火灾风险增加</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australias-southeast-sweats-heatwave-lifting-bushfire-risk-2024-03-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周六，澳大利亚大片地区经历了严重的热浪天气，导致该国东南部发生丛林火灾的风险增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australias-southeast-sweats-heatwave-lifting-bushfire-risk-2024-03-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 00:00:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据彭博社报道，台积电将为美国一家芯片工厂赢得超过 50 亿美元的资助</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-win-more-than-5-billion-grants-us-chip-plant-bloomberg-reports-2024-03-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社周五报道，全球最大的代工芯片制造商台积电 (TSMC) 将从美国政府获得超过 50 亿美元的联邦拨款，用于在亚利桑那州建立一家芯片制造工厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-win-more-than-5-billion-grants-us-chip-plant-bloomberg-reports-2024-03-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 17:27:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度开始驱逐第一批逃离 2021 年政变的缅甸难民</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-deports-first-group-myanmar-refugees-who-fled-2021-coup-2024-03-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度于周五开始驱逐第一批在 2021 年军事政变后寻求庇护的缅甸难民，并计划在未来几天内遣返更多难民，几周前印度表示将终止与缅甸的免签证边境政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-deports-first-group-myanmar-refugees-who-fled-2021-coup-2024-03-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 14:49:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>MH370航班乘客的儿子因纪念死者而发生冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/son-flight-mh370-passenger-conflicted-over-honouring-dead-2024-03-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[每年春天，中国都会庆祝清明节，家人都会去祭扫祖先的坟墓，祭奠祖先。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/son-flight-mh370-passenger-conflicted-over-honouring-dead-2024-03-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 11:20:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国提高年轻医生薪酬，否认医疗保健陷入危机</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-improve-young-doctors-pay-denies-healthcare-is-crisis-2024-03-08/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国政府周五表示，计划迅速采取措施改善年轻医生的薪酬和工作条件，以满足离职医疗实习生的一项关键要求，但否认存在全面的医疗危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-improve-young-doctors-pay-denies-healthcare-is-crisis-2024-03-08/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 09:07:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
